profile content: Dr. Mario Alberto Almanza Reyes, a Tijuana bariatric professional, is an acting surgeon to the Mexican Social Security Institute. He acts as a Regional Hospital 1 Surgeon and is respected among the professionals there.Dr. Almanza earned two medical degrees from the Autonomous University of Baja California, the second of which he graduated with in 2007, and has performed more than 15,000 surgeries since completing his university education.
